Lightweight Libraries in C++

This is a lightweight C++ libraries, mainly based on header files only,
for the personal use.

Version 0.1
currently this library contains only logstream class, which supports
for a output stream toward both cout and ofstream simultanously. 
it also supports switching function to turn on and off either of them.

Version 0.2
multi-dimensional array and circular buffer class templates are added.

This library is distributed under LGPL license. Please read LICENSE
file for detailed information.
